{"tid":1658582,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[新牌]Hyundai i30 vs Golf 280 vs A3 Sportback","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T12:07:03.000Z","uid":52696,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"961fe403954ec37e248e1e885a88779b803d33a0","tid":1658582,"uid":52696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"新牌想買架細車 budget約&lt;25萬<br />\n最多4個人坐 唔要求好快既速度 想慳油易揸為主<br />\n上網睇完資料揀左呢三部<br />\n<br />\n <strong>Hyundai i30 </strong>$23萬<br />\n-齊設備 <br />\n-大天窗<br />\n-冷暖電皮座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-內籠有啲膠<br />\n<br />\n<strong>golf 280 </strong>$24萬<br />\n-傳統錶板<br />\n-無皮座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>A3 Sportback</strong> $29萬 / 二手 約20萬頭(2017)<br />\n-外表型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-內籠靚過i30同golf<br />\n<br />\n巴打們會係呢3架入邊揀邊架？或者仲有無其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n題外話 係街從未見過i30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760e82da61689e8d0cbbb10a7f79fcdac0d3d1d8","tid":1658582,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3799015c6d19fa70f662db99358550425d862b35","tid":1658582,"uid":316473,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"睇你篇文你都係想要A3架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c49f6f62404ae240bfbf4940c8a8241e374f54","tid":1658582,"uid":52696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3799015c6d19fa70f662db99358550425d862b35","tid":1658582,"uid":316473,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"睇你篇文你都係想要A3架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:59:42.000Z","msg":"golf無皮坐真係卻步 <br />\n但i30同A3有啲難揀<br />\ni30好似無咩review..."},{"pid":"ea908dfccdf45aea387d15ab2b5a7e2dfcf99ff5","tid":1658582,"uid":66590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"i30 拍車男有review"},{"pid":"53ed08c8403a58684a1cdaaca81a93fcb09c016e","tid":1658582,"uid":237707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:19:24.000Z","msg":"渣緊2016 A3 sportback (上大昌買二手)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都新牌 之前都考慮過 Golf 同 A3 (韓國車就冇考慮過)<br />\n<br />\n買之前都去車展睇過2018 A3, 好似28萬, 同我依家呢部比, 2018版多左平底軚盤, 撥片, 動態方向燈 (個人覺得幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n渣落差唔多10個月, 總結下:<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港冬天我都好少用到開暖氣, 熱凳我覺得冇用 (反而想要冷氣凳, 但未見到邊隻同級車有)<br />\n<br />\n2. 我大部分都係坐兩個人, 後座好少坐, 有朋友坐過後面覺得窄<br />\n<br />\n3. 係停車場自己炒過, 轉彎貼柱, 搞到爆後胎+凹門, 諗清楚短期內會有整車嘅可能<br />\n<br />\n4. 電凳有用, 成日會換人渣, 較番張凳唔使手動咁麻煩 (當然有埋set記憶坐位最正)"},{"pid":"2edb6173fa0c82d68d1f4072e5eb2fb03384ea09","tid":1658582,"uid":217332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:46:06.000Z","msg":"Golf 就出新款"},{"pid":"d17792851a3b1db5fe2e7908e5304546a08d2d4e","tid":1658582,"uid":194791,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:46:45.000Z","msg":"現代 I 30n 性價比好高"},{"pid":"7b8411d537bd4b52ccc8637381459b56a81f5d38","tid":1658582,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"2017年A3 好似唔洗咁貴"},{"pid":"23d92a7b0e2b5e39267685e62789f193e4629660","tid":1658582,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"A3 跌價快喎"},{"pid":"de37a9183d832482cc41a00f0f4c57cc6529271b","tid":1658582,"uid":122534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:04:53.000Z","msg":"i30 最多設備 性價比高 仲有後冷氣風口<br />\n3架最好揸係A3,隔音方面會咁排 A3 -&gt; i30 最差係golf<br />\ngolf 同 A3 都揸過,揸A3 Hatchback 2017 既動態好過golf 同唔似揸FF 車 <br />\n要多功能揀i30 好操控A3 舒服我覺得2架差唔多"},{"pid":"c366fd4d584fd250510664b9abbc6ce5c94e6d6d","tid":1658582,"uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:38:10.000Z","msg":"i30揸嘅時候除非你係sport mode<br />\n如果唔係畀油去嘅時候係要等一等先去<br />\n但問題唔嚴重。"},{"pid":"c0b7549d6a677d3073792514c883c45e32032411","tid":1658582,"uid":97181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"揸緊A3 2017款 Hatchback<br />\n最慳油係行高速，最高紀錄果程做過4.6L/100km，同cylinder on demand有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n部車好適合新牌揸，舒適但避震唔會太軟<br />\n轉向靈活軚感都夠，係hill start比較遲鈍，成日比後車砵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n空間方面前座就好舒服，後面的腿部空間係的確細，高過170坐落去係會辛苦，所以高的朋友通常都要坐前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於後面擺嘢就一般啦，無咩特別<br />\n<br />\nbtw自己整花部車好難，咁細部車都整得花要好好鍛煉自己技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申聽日甩P<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6178728cf3ccd46b4fdf7128f944986e7486f4ab","tid":1658582,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"加少少i30N"},{"pid":"74f4a47edbb27489602f8b2e326d9016a8a38988","tid":1658582,"uid":237707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0b7549d6a677d3073792514c883c45e32032411","tid":1658582,"uid":97181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"揸緊A3 2017款 Hatchback<br />\n最慳油係行高速，最高紀錄果程做過4.6L/100km，同cylinder on demand有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n部車好適合新牌揸，舒適但避震唔會太軟<br />\n轉向靈活軚感都夠，係hill start比較遲鈍，成日比後車砵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n空間方面前座就好舒服，後面的腿部空間係的確細，高過170坐落去係會辛苦，所以高的朋友通常都要坐前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於後面擺嘢就一般啦，無咩特別<br />\n<br />\nbtw自己整花部車好難，咁細部車都整得花要好好鍛煉自己技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申聽日甩P<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:40:35.000Z","